snippet.title: Warframe | The Old Blood: Fight the Kuva Lich
snippet.description:
Available now on PC, The Old Blood update delivers a completely new breed of enemy, difficulty and reward: the Kuva Lich.

Face off against an immortal threat whose sole existence evolves for one purpose -- taking you down. Upgrade your new Parazon hidden blade to end the cycle...or convert this vengeful foe into a powerful ally. Learn more: http://wrfr.me/oldblood
